WEBVTT

00:06.959 --> 00:10.124
Previously on Mars.

00:10.125 --> 00:11.999
When you believe
in a goal the way we believed

00:12.000 --> 00:15.165
in Mars, conviction alone
will sustain you through

00:15.166 --> 00:17.791
almost any test.

00:17.792 --> 00:18.999
Robert!

00:19.000 --> 00:22.791
If you find evidence
of a second genesis.

00:22.792 --> 00:25.290
Evolution can begin again.

00:25.291 --> 00:27.332
I've got faith.

00:27.333 --> 00:29.207
You know,
I used to stand in the doorway

00:29.208 --> 00:31.165
of the farmhouse where I
grew up looking at all of the

00:31.166 --> 00:33.874
crops, thinking about
all the people they'd feed.

00:33.875 --> 00:35.457
If you push too hard too fast,

00:35.458 --> 00:37.791
something's gonna break.

00:37.792 --> 00:41.542
If they fail, everyone's out.

00:42.291 --> 00:45.040
But faith
doesn't guarantee success.

00:45.041 --> 00:48.374
Without plants we're nothing.

00:48.375 --> 00:52.583
The real test is
what happens when you fail.

